Ingredients:
 - 1/4 cup milk
 - 1/4 cup berries of your choice (strawberry works well)
 - 2 big fresh bananas (approx 400g or more)
 - 200g Quark (dairy product)
 - 15g honey
 - optional: 2 cups of milk

Directions:
  1. Put all ingredients into a vertical-mounted blender.
  2. Blend it till it becomes soft, creamy texture with no hard pieces.
  3. Optional: move the resulting dessert into a bowl, pour 2 cups of milk and add 1-2 spoons of dessert to the milk. Blend for 30 seconds for milk shake.